OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FThe families of the Nottingham attack
OL,7,Fvictims say there were "missed
OL,8,Fopportunities" to stop the killer,
OL,9,Fwith questions now being asked about
OL,10,Fwhy he was not under closer
OL,11,Fsupervision.
OL,13,FDr Sanjoy Kumar, the father of 19-year-
OL,14,Fold victim Grace O'Malley-Kumar, said
OL,15,Fthe "missed opportunities to divert
OL,16,Fhis lethal path" will "forever play on
OL,17,Four minds."
