OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FValdo Calocane, 32, fatally stabbed
OL,7,Fstudents Grace and Barnaby Webber and
OL,8,F65-year-old school caretaker Ian
OL,9,FCoates in Nottingham city centre in
OL,10,Fthe early hours of 13 June 2023.
OL,12,Fat a hearing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,13,Fon Tuesday, on the grounds of
OL,14,Fdiminished responsibility due to
OL,15,F"serious" mental illness. Calocane has
OL,16,Fparanoid schizophrenia.
OL,18,FHe also admitted three counts of
OL,19,Fattempted murder relating to
OL,20,Fpedestrians he deliberately targeted
OL,21,Fwith Mr Coates' van.
