OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,F"Our darling son, his dear friend
OL,7,FGrace, and a wonderfully kind
OL,8,Fgrandfather Ian, have been stolen from
OL,9,Fus forever, and have been let down by
OL,10,Fthe very system that should have been
OL,11,Fprotecting them."
OL,13,FJames Coates, whose father Ian Coates
OL,14,Fwas killed, said that "failures from
OL,15,Fthe police, the CPS, the health
OL,16,Fservice" had lead to the three
OL,17,Fkillings.
