OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FCalocane was discharged from Highbury
OL,7,FHospital into the care of Nottingham
OL,8,FCity Crisis and advised to take
OL,9,Fmedication for a minimum of 6 to 9
OL,10,Fmonths and to seek medical advice, if
OL,11,Fhe wished to stop taking it.
OL,13,FCalocane was readmitted to hospital
OL,14,Fafter attempting to force his way into
OL,15,Fa flat, having stopped taking his
OL,16,Fmedication.JHe then evaded contact
OL,17,Fwith the community team.
