OL,12,Finpatient and discharged on February
OL,13,F24 2022.
OL,15,FHe was then reviewed in an outpatient
OL,16,Fclinic and in July 2022 claimed, it is
OL,17,Fbelieved falsely, that he was not in
OL,18,Fthe country.
