OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FJust weeks before the attacks in
OL,7,FNottingham, Calocane attacked two
OL,8,Fcolleagues at a warehouse at Kegworth
OL,9,Fin Leicestershire. After that
OL,10,Fincident, attempts were made to
OL,11,Fcontact him to tell him he was not
OL,12,Fallowed back on the premises, but he
OL,13,Fdidn't respond.
OL,15,FCalocane killed students Barnaby and
OL,16,FGrace, before killing Ian - a 65-year-
OL,17,Fold caretaker.
