OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News,
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police's Assistant
OL,8,FChief Constable Rob Griffin said that
OL,9,Fit would have been"very difficult to
OL,10,Fhave done anything differently", and
OL,11,Fadded: "We constantly debrief these
OL,12,Fkinds of operations, we've pored over
OL,13,Fthe detail, pored over the way that we
OL,14,Fresponded, the way that we started the
OL,15,Finvestigation from the outset.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/22
