OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,F"I'm really confident that everything
OL,7,Fwe did was thorough and professional.
OL,8,FI wouldn't have looked to change
OL,9,Fanything and, tragically, we couldn't
OL,10,Fhave stopped any of what happened on
OL,11,Fthat night."
OL,13,FCalocane was arrested early that
OL,14,Fmorning - Mr Griffin noted "the
OL,15,FIlkeston Road killings of Grace and
OL,16,FBarnaby were at around 4am, and not
OL,17,Flong after at 5.30am we'd arrested
OL,18,Fhim".
