OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FHe said: "I think it was fast-moving,
OL,7,Fbut we arrested him as quickly as we
OL,8,Fcould."
OL,10,FMr Griffin added that he knew Calocane
OL,11,F"was sectioned, so admitted into
OL,12,Fmental health hospitals on at least
OL,13,Ffour occasions, and we the police
OL,14,Fsupported our mental health colleagues
OL,15,Fon numerous occasions in taking him to
OL,16,Fthose hospitals."
