OL,6,FHe stated: "From a criminal
OL,7,Fperspective, a criminal history
OL,8,Fperspective, it is right to say that
OL,9,Fhe doesn't have any convictions, he
OL,10,Fdoesn't have any cautions or
OL,11,Freprimands."
OL,13,FHowever, in a later statement released
OL,14,Fthe day of sentencing, Thursday 25
OL,15,FJanuary, Mr Griffin clarified his
OL,16,Fearlier comments.
