OL,3,CWere there 'missed opportunities' in
OL,4,Cthe lead up to the Nottingham attacks?
OL,6,FMr Majid continued: "We always aim to
OL,7,Fcare for people in the least
OL,8,Frestrictive way and to support people
OL,9,Fto live well in their own homes and
OL,10,Fsociety. If a patient no longer
OL,11,Fengages with our services and support
OL,12,Fand they do not meet criteria to be
OL,13,Fdetained under the Mental Health Act,
OL,14,Fthey are discharged back to the care
OL,15,Fof their GP and can be referred back
OL,16,Finto our services at any time.
